{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"msg_OrLSTekVJ2vegguubKnPYHY5","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"tool_OJpdcrkUjwKRHg8I5sxCe7wN","name":"Task","input":{"description":"PRD reviewer subagent for TST-001","prompt":"You are the feature-dev-aidd:prd-reviewer subagent for ticket TST-001.\n\n## Your Task\nReview the PRD at `/Users/griogrii_riabov/grigorii_projects/ai_advent_challenge_new/aidd/docs/prd/TST-001.prd.md` and provide a structured review focusing on:\n\n1. **PRD Completeness**: Check all required sections are present and meaningful\n2. **Placeholder Detection**: Identify any template/placeholder text that should be removed\n3. **Narrative vs Structured Consistency**: Check if narrative text conflicts with AIDD:ANSWERS, AIDD:DECISIONS, etc.\n4. **Requirements Quality**: Verify functional/non-functional requirements are specific and testable\n5. **Acceptance Criteria**: Check ACs are clear and verifiable\n\n## PRD Review Report Output\nProduce findings in this format:\n```json\n{\n  \"ticket\": \"TST-001\",\n  \"overall_status\": \"ready|warn|blocked\",\n  \"verdict\": \"APPROVED|PENDING_CHANGES|BLOCKED\",\n  \"findings\": [\n    {\n      \"severity\": \"critical|major|minor|info\",\n      \"category\": \"placeholder|consistency|completeness|clarity\",\n      \"location\": \"section name or line reference\",\n      \"issue\": \"description of the issue\",\n      \"recommendation\": \"how to fix\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"action_items\": [\n    \"specific actionable item to fix\"\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## Key Issues to Check\n1. Lines with: `> Используй только compact формат` - this is template help text, should be removed\n2. Lines with: `> Номера Q синхронизируй` - this is template help text, should be removed\n3. Narrative says \"WebSocket push-обновления\" but Q5 answer is \"Polling\" - mismatch\n4. Section 8 still says \"WebSocket push notifications infrastructure\" but should be \"Polling\"\n\nOutput your review results to stdout.",