{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"tool_nYmFOX48TrIynpDUBZCGbWQ0","type":"tool_result","content":"    35→## AIDD:DECISIONS\n    36→- **Auth Model**: Current system uses X-Profile-Key and X-Profile-Auth headers, not JWT\n    37→- **State Management**: Frontend uses Zustand (not Redux) with persistence\n    38→- **Real-time**: SSE already implemented for flows/MCP; WebSocket needs new infrastructure\n    39→- **Role Storage**: Roles stored in profile document (see profileTypes.ts: `roles: z.array(z.string())`)\n    40→\n    41→## AIDD:INTEGRATION_POINTS\n    42→\n    43→### Backend Integration Points\n    44→\n    45→1. **Profile Header Extraction** (`/Users/griogrii_riabov/grigorii_projects/ai_advent_challenge_new/frontend/src/lib/profileStore.ts:92-110`)\n    46→   - `buildActiveProfileHeaders()` creates headers: X-Profile-Key, X-Profile-Channel, X-Profile-Auth\n    47→   - Backend must read these headers for identity\n    48→\n    49→2. **API Client** (`/Users/griogrii_riabov/grigorii_projects/ai_advent_challenge_new/frontend/src/lib/apiClient.ts`)\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c7744ce0-fdf6-47dd-ae34-edb35fc5dbd2","uuid":"32e1df76-bf29-4b8a-af5b-260d08022900","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/griogrii_riabov/grigorii_projects/ai_advent_challenge_new/aidd/docs/research/TST-001.md","content":"## AIDD:DECISIONS\n- **Auth Model**: Current system uses X-Profile-Key and X-Profile-Auth headers, not JWT\n- **State Management**: Frontend uses Zustand (not Redux) with persistence\n- **Real-time**: SSE already implemented for flows/MCP; WebSocket needs new infrastructure\n- **Role Storage**: Roles stored in profile document (see profileTypes.ts: `roles: z.array(z.string())`)\n\n## AIDD:INTEGRATION_POINTS\n\n### Backend Integration Points\n\n1. **Profile Header Extraction** (`/Users/griogrii_riabov/grigorii_projects/ai_advent_challenge_new/frontend/src/lib/profileStore.ts:92-110`)\n   - `buildActiveProfileHeaders()` creates headers: X-Profile-Key, X-Profile-Channel, X-Profile-Auth\n   - Backend must read these headers for identity\n\n2. **API Client** (`/Users/griogrii_riabov/grigorii_projects/ai_advent_challenge_new/frontend/src/lib/apiClient.ts`)","numLines":15,"startLine":35,"totalLines":278}}}
